d5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.dzhabue57wcx-1024x509.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.dzhabue57wcx-300x149.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.dzhabue57wcx-768x382.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.dzhabue57wcx-jpg.webp 1281w" width="1024" height="509" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.qioh905j87g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.qioh905j87g-1024x509.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.qioh905j87g-1024x509.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.qioh905j87g-300x149.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.qioh905j87g-768x382.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.qioh905j87g-jpg.webp 1281w" width="1024" height="509" /></a></p><p> mocopi PC应用程序计划于6月13日（星期四）发布。 PC 应用程序允许您通过智能手机迷你应用程序“mocopi link”在 PC 上捕捉动作、保存、预览和发送动作，该应用程序接收传感器数据并将其重新发送到您的 PC。轻松与其他 PC 软件集成，并扩展可支持的智能手机数量。</p><p>它还与头像操作应用程序“ <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1364390/Animaze_by_FaceRig/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Animaz by FaceRig</a> ”配合使用，允许发送 mocopi 运动数据，允许将面部和身体结合起来的表情。还将预装三个 RAYNOS-chan 头像。</p><p>此外，未来我们计划扩大兼容运动格式的范围，并支持直接连接PC。</p><p>有两种价格计划：允许您使用动态查看功能的“免费计划”和允许您使用 mocopi 全部功能的“基本计划”。基本套餐每月费用为 550 日元。分发目的地是 Microsoft Store。</p><h2>最新更新信息</h2><p>mocopi更新进一步扩展了使用场景，提高了使用VR时的跟踪精度，并添加了上半身集中模式。 5月30日发布的mocopi ver2.1.0有以下更新。</p><blockquote><p>・连接传感器时的精度反馈 ・按下传感器按钮即可重置姿势 ・位置重置 ・运动预览期间的背景变化 ・加载用 mocopi 以外的工具记录的运动文件 (BVH)</p></blockquote><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.txchkvpign5z-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.txchkvpign5z-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 920px) 100vw, 920px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.txchkvpign5z-jpg.webp 920w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.txchkvpign5z-300x242.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.txchkvpign5z-768x619.webp 768w" width="920" height="742" /></a></p><p>通过按下传感器按钮进行姿势重置/位置重置现在允许通过按下传感器按钮进行姿势重置/位置重置，而无需操作 mocopi 应用程序屏幕。您可以通过按左手腕传感器（WRIST/L）按钮来“重置姿势”，通过按右手腕传感器（WRIST/R）按钮来“重置位置”。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.wqflow3ev3mv-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.wqflow3ev3mv-1024x468.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.wqflow3ev3mv-1024x468.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.wqflow3ev3mv-300x137.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.wqflow3ev3mv-768x351.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.wqflow3ev3mv-jpg.webp 1281w" width="1024" height="468" /></a></p><p>同一天，我们提供了使用 mocopi 传感器数据的 SDK 和示例应用程序。 “mocopi传感器数据读取器”是一款适用于Android/iOS的SDK，可以访问mocopi的传感器数据，让开发者可以灵活地使用传感器数据。 “mocopi 数据分析器”是一个可视化 mocopi 传感器数据的示例应用程序。</p><h2>举办支持创作者的活动</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.b3lzjk1dvy00-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.b3lzjk1dvy00-1024x552.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.b3lzjk1dvy00-1024x552.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.b3lzjk1dvy00-300x162.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.b3lzjk1dvy00-768x414.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.b3lzjk1dvy00-jpg.webp 1281w" width="1024" height="552" /></a></p><p>创作者支援活动将持续到8月9日（星期五），如果在索尼商店购买mocopi，将获得5,500日元的折扣。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.24iuxlofgl8e-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.24iuxlofgl8e-1024x553.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.24iuxlofgl8e-1024x553.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.24iuxlofgl8e-300x162.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.24iuxlofgl8e-768x415.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/0f1484fa2bd5ae071d30598470f10591-kix.24iuxlofgl8e-jpg.webp 1281w" width="1024" height="553" /></a></p><p>还将举办视频比赛。申请条件是使用mocopi制作时长不超过3分钟的视频，详情将于稍后在官网和<a href="https://x.com/raynosbySony" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Official X（原Twitter）</a>上公布。</p><p><a href="https://www.sony.jp/mocopi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>官方网站在这里</strong></a></p><p>（参考）官方提供的材料</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/mocopi-pc-application/">期待已久的移动动作捕捉PC应用程序“mocopi”已经发布了！</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上