40x2160-1024x576.png 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-06-09_16-42-21.423_3840x2160-768x432.png 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-06-09_16-42-21.423_3840x2160-1536x864.png 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-06-09_16-42-21.423_3840x2160-2048x1152.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 3840px) 100vw, 3840px" /></a></p><p></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.xygf39p21em7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.xygf39p21em7-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.xygf39p21em7-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.xygf39p21em7-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.xygf39p21em7-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.xygf39p21em7-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.xygf39p21em7-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> VRChat实例的最大数量是80人，但是通过同步其他实例中观众的动作，<strong>可以使其看起来好像400人聚集在一起。这是</strong>上次谈到的一项神秘技术。既可以享受VR的舒适感，又可以享受真人聚集在一起的节日感觉，真是太棒了。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bvma4wawq3fr-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bvma4wawq3fr-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bvma4wawq3fr-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5