78416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.qqp0bit7zt1c-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>最后副歌部分<strong>，舞台透过壮丽的夕阳天空飞向远方</strong>，太棒了，因为这让我感觉我可以去任何地方，就像歌词说的那样！ 您可以享受高品质的简单 VR 体验。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ykhytxxk6q9b-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7y8zreqm1zyl-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>现在Showcase现场表演的第一首和第二首歌曲已经结束，这是本次现场表演中首次表演的部分。</p><p> CIEL酱说<strong>：“我会引导你进入我内心的世界。”</strong></p><p>呃，在哪里？ ？ 正当我这么想着的时候，突然眼前的一切都变成了白色……</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2mu6w1s0fkau-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 1.64em;">我身处一个完全陌生的空间。</span></strong></p><p><strong>这是……？ ？ ？</strong></p><p>更何况，刚才还在的大量观众都消失了，<strong>我们被传送到了一个只有十人左右的狭小空间。</strong> （后来发现根据空间的不同，人数也不同，而我恰好在一个人少的空间。）</p><p>第三首歌<strong>《Horawa》</strong>突然在迷茫又感人的观众耳中回响。这是 KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO 所属歌手 Rime 的歌曲的翻唱。</p><p>舞台就像一个鸟笼和一个石坛，漂浮在漆黑的天空中。 CIEL酱站在中央，周围环绕着大花。</p><p><strong>关闭！</strong> <strong>CIEL酱感觉非常接近</strong>，可能是因为与观众一侧几乎没有高度差异。<br />真的感觉自己进入了CIEL酱的心里。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.326dvuq32qc7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.326dvuq32qc7-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.326dvuq32qc7-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.326dvuq32qc7-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.326dvuq32qc7-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.326dvuq32qc7-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.326dvuq32qc7-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8aylqzy2jk5m-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8aylqzy2jk5m-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8aylqzy2jk5m-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8aylqzy2jk5m-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8aylqzy2jk5m-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8aylqzy2jk5m-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8aylqzy2jk5m-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hyaqvmom26ii-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hyaqvmom26ii-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hyaqvmom26ii-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hyaqvmom26ii-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hyaqvmom26ii-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hyaqvmom26ii-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hyaqvmom26ii-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p><strong>黑暗中花朵色彩斑斓、温柔的光芒与音乐配合</strong>得恰到好处，有一种倦怠的魅力。 CIEL酱本身从内部发出微弱的光，光的颜色会随着声音而变化。空间制作很创新，使用包括歌手在内的整个建筑作为照明。</p><p><strong>只有右手发出柔和光芒的制作</strong>也很新鲜，营造出真正美丽而梦幻的时刻。原本一头雾水的观众听得入迷……</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7eb48hfet3g1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7eb48hfet3g1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.mogurav