ps://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.j1copnd2fr7i-1-169x300.webp 169w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.j1copnd2fr7i-1-768x1365.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.j1copnd2fr7i-1-864x1536.webp 864w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.j1copnd2fr7i-1-jpg.webp 900w" width="576" height="1024" /></a></p><p>我也是这么想的，但第四首歌是<strong>《Mini no Suspicion》。</strong></p><p> “别发光，我只是好奇。”</p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 1.64em;">巴里！ ！ ！</span></strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>当CIEL酱开始唱歌并甩开手臂的那一刻，</p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 1.64em;">空间如同雷霆劈下，崩裂开来！ ！ ！ ！</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 1.64em;">惊喜！ ！ ！ ！</span></strong></p><p>这首歌绝对比CIEL酱的歌曲更黑暗、更激烈，气氛瞬间就变了。不知不觉间<strong>，雨从头顶倾盆而下，碎玻璃漂浮在空间中，将随着声音而快速切换的灯光反射得耀眼夺目</strong>。透过雨滴和玻璃上的倒影，可以看到CIEL严肃的表情。玻璃闪闪发光，仿佛随着歌曲的快节奏而跳动，它在太空中翱翔，仿佛失重。<br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.nlxxayxk3kwz-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.nlxxayxk3kwz-576x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.nlxxayxk3kwz-576x1024.webp 576w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.nlxxayxk3kwz-169x300.webp 169w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.nlxxayxk3kwz-768x1365.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.nlxxayxk3kwz-864x1536.webp 864w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.nlxxayxk3kwz-jpg.webp 900w" width="576" height="1024" /></a></p><p><strong>不，信息太多了……！ ！</strong></p><p>我跟不上发展的步伐。随着CIEL动情的歌声，玻璃多次破碎，漂浮在空中，猛烈的雷雨开始了。她的外表就像是<strong>一个能够掌控天空的女巫</strong>。而<strong>我们观众只能在其中来回穿梭……！</strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ruvmibrimx31-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ruvmibrimx31-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ruvmibrimx31-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ruvmibrimx31-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ruvmibrimx31-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ruvmibrimx31-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ruvmibrimx31-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.49v9ww283436-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.49v9ww283436-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.49v9ww283436-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.49v9ww283436-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.49v9ww283436-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.49v9ww283436-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.49v9ww283436-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2wa8p9gzmx91-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2wa8p9gzmx91-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2wa8p9gzmx91-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2wa8p9gzmx91-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2wa8p9gzmx91-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2wa8p9gzmx91-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2wa8p9gzmx91-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>我看过很多 VR 现场表演，但这是我第一次看到同时包含如此多反射和光表达的现场表演。对于技术我是个业余爱好者，但产量足以让我想知道<strong>“加工是怎么回事……？”</strong>因为CIEL和风景都倒映在每一个破碎的玻璃里。那太糟了……。</p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 1.64em;">是不是很难相信这不是MV的截图，而是VR直播时实时拍摄的图像……？</span></strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.9kzavnhqlrm7-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>从此，意想不到的空间转变再次发生！在第五首歌曲<strong>《少年漫画》</strong>中，CIEL酱降落在一个看起来像由许多块组成的巨大舞台的舞台上。<strong>美丽的聚光灯！</strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.v68e2h4d9egt-jpg.webp 1600w" width