strong>出现并在舞台上自由飞翔，也相当漂亮。复杂的性能。</p><p><strong>太自由了……！ ！这是一场“奇幻剧”……！</strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.bubfk9v6ysj1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.wa7h26kce15-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>即使在可以自由设计空间的VR现场表演中，准备舞台之类的东西来体验表演也是标准的。<br />另一方面，我觉得很少有作品能够破坏整个空间，<strong>将整个观众扔进一个代表歌曲世界观的空间中</strong>。一部不将舞台和观众席分开，将歌手和观众都作为舞台设备一部分的制作，可以说是充分利用了VR沉浸感的制作。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080.png"><img data-dominant-color="38426c" data-has-transparency="false" style="--dominant-color: #38426c;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="not-transparent alignnone size-full wp-image-252446" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080.png 1920w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080-300x169.png 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080-1024x576.png 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080-768x432.png 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-26-34.694_1920x1080-1536x864.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080.png"><img data-dominant-color="444649" data-has-transparency="false" style="--dominant-color: #444649;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="not-transparent alignnone size-full wp-image-252447" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080.png 1920w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080-300x169.png 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080-1024x576.png 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080-768x432.png 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-22-21.726_1920x1080-1536x864.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-18-43.485_1920x1080.png"><img data-dominant-color="242420" data-has-transparency="false" style="--dominant-color: #242420;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="not-transparent alignnone size-full wp-image-252445" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-18-43.485_1920x1080.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-18-43.485_1920x1080.png 1920w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-18-43.485_1920x1080-300x169.png 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-18-43.485_1920x1080-1024x576.png 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-18-43.485_1920x1080-768x432.png 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/VRChat_2024-05-18_20-18-43.485_1920x1080-1536x864.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></a>带着压倒性的沉浸感，进行最后的空间转换。 （看到地板像块一样下沉，这有点有趣）</p><p>当我回到会场时，我发现自己的座位与开始时不同！ 这很好，因为如果你换个座位，你会看到不同的景色。</p><p>当CIEL酱说“只剩下两首歌了！”时，观众们兴​​奋地挥手致意。期待已久的首张专辑也宣布发行，<strong>全场沸腾，尽管他们保持沉默</strong>。 CIEL酱看起来很高兴并感谢她。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ugsb1pjbd7wm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ugsb1pjbd7wm-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ugsb1pjbd7wm-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ugsb1pjbd7wm-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.ugsb1pjbd7wm-