loads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zd3jwt3ws3rn-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zd3jwt3ws3rn-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zd3jwt3ws3rn-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zd3jwt3ws3rn-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>歌曲结束时，CIEL酱说了声<strong>“谢谢！！”</strong> ，同时<strong>发行了银色磁带！ ！</strong>这场意想不到的惊喜表演，让会场的热闹达到了顶峰。<br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8j3haevdowo7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8j3haevdowo7-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8j3haevdowo7-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8j3haevdowo7-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8j3haevdowo7-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8j3haevdowo7-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8j3haevdowo7-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hv61eypl7wf2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hv61eypl7wf2-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hv61eypl7wf2-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2