s://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6xm4mvijvojf-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6xm4mvijvojf-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6xm4mvijvojf-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6xm4mvijvojf-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6xm4mvijvojf-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>第六首歌结束了，到了最后一首歌的时间了。她害羞地说：“我付出了太多的努力。”（可爱......），但在喝水休息后，CIEL回顾了她自2021年出道以来的道路。</p><p>感谢大家对我的热情支持，让我能够进行各种活动，我会谈谈迄今为止我对歌曲的感受以及导致我中断的原因。他告诉现场的歌迷，他真的很高兴能遇见CIEL、被CIEL唱歌、被CIEL爱，并继续唱最后一首歌<strong>，“我感谢所有给予我爱的人，我很高兴”。我会用我所有的感情来唱歌。”</strong>我做到了。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.u1w11zrd0ltg-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.zfz968u6yw5u-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>第七首歌是<strong>《Kimi no Kishi, Kimi no Wish》</strong> 。这是一首适合作为最后一首歌的歌曲，因为它蕴含着强烈的对亲人的关怀之情。</p><p>随着小CIEL飘逸透明的歌声，<strong>花瓣般的白光聚集飞扬起来，笼罩了整个会场</strong>。我感觉到，在绘制轨迹时起飞的许多温暖的灯光中，充满了小CIEL的感情。<br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-576x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-576x1024.webp 576w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-169x300.webp 169w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-768x1365.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-864x1536.webp 864w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.sfgrzji4j8zw-jpg.webp 900w" width="576" height="1024" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.3cltvs7bfr58-jpg.webp" tar